    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Drinking beakers characterised by small masses of glass, often in the form of round blobs or tear-drop shapes, applied to the body primarily for decorative purposes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
